CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B6, reads: "DOCTOR OF MEDICINE - Ahmed Samuel Milai Jr., some of one of The Courier's art editors, became a Doctor of Medicine when he received his diploma at the University of Pittsburgh."
TitMainTitle: Ahmed Samuel Milai Jr. wearing doctoral robe and mortar board, after receiving Doctor of Medicine degree, for University of Pittsburgh graduation
